pageContext.claim: “My son Donald openly gave his e-mails to the media & authorities whereas Crooked Hillary Clinton deleted (& acid washed) her 33,000 e-mails!”
pageContext.analysis: Donald Trump Jr. only released the emails facing a pending report on the content of the emails by the New York Times. The emails were deleted with a free software program known as BleachBit; it is no such thing as "acid washed."
